                        <h1>Which oil for your Infiniti</h1>
                        <h2>Infiniti engine oil</h2>
                        <p xmlns="">There are a full range of Mobil branded engine oils suitable for the different ranges of Infiniti cars, including oils suitable for gasoline engines and oils suitable for hybrid engines. There are Mobil branded engine oils engineered to be suitable for Infiniti Q50 models such as the Infiniti Q50 S as well as oils suitable for the Infiniti QX60 models such as the Infiniti QX60 Coupe.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <strong>5W-30 engine oils for Infiniti</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">Mobil 1 5W-30 is an advanced synthetic engine oil that meets or exceeds the industry specifications for your Infiniti: ILSAC GF-5 and API SN.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <br>

                            <strong>How does synthetic oil help to protect my Infiniti&rsquo;s engine?</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">Tests show that Mobil 1 can reach all moving parts of the engine faster than some conventional oils. Until your oil circulates fully, friction between dry parts of the engine will slowly reduce the life of the engine. Synthetic engine oils like Mobil 1 start circulating right away, protecting every moving part within the engine, and over time this can translate into savings in maintenance costs.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">
                            <br>

                            <strong>Which oil should I buy for my Infiniti?</strong>
                        </p>

                        <p xmlns="">It is important to use the right oil in your car to comply with the Infiniti&rsquo;s manufacturer specifications. Using the right Mobil 1 product during routine servicing and according to your vehicle&rsquo;s handbook will not affect the Infiniti manufacturer&rsquo;s warranty.</p>
